<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>القوم بثَقَلِهم، قال <span class="c2">«١»</span>:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَتَذَكَّرَا ثَقَلًا رَثِيداً بَعْدَ ما ... أَلْقَتْ ذُكَاءُ يَمِينَها في كَافِر<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">والثَّقَلان:</span> الجن والإِنس،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أَيُّهَ الثَّقَلاانِ <span class="c2">«٢»</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>و <span class="c4">[فَعَلَة]</span>، بالهاء<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[ل]</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[ثَقَلَة]</span>: يقال: وجد ثَقَلَة في جسده:<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وهي ما يجده من ثِقَل الطعام.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>و <span class="c4">[فَعِلَة]</span>، بكسر العين<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[ل]</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[ثَقِلَة]</span>: يقال: ارتحل القوم بثَقِلَتِهم وثقَلهم: أي بأمتعتهم كلها.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
